BNY Mellon Sued by U.S. Attorney’s Office Over Foreign Exchange Services

-- B y   M i c h a e l   H y t h a
-- 
2011-10-05T00:13:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/bny-mellon-sued-by-u-s-attorney-s-office-over-foreign-exchange-services.html
  Bank of New York Mellon Corp. (BK)  was
sued by the U.S. Attorney’s office in  Manhattan  over accusations
it defrauded clients using its foreign exchange services for
more than 10 years.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michael Hytha at 
 mhytha@bloomberg.net  